Interface ICategory

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddonCategory, CustomizationCategory, DatapackCategory, ModCategory, ModpackCategory, PluginCategory, ResourcepackCategory, ShaderCategory, WorldCategory
public interface ICategory
Interface ICategory is a representation of a Minecraft category and is used to group Integrations.
